snippet.title: JumpStart Preschool Full Playthrough (Classic 1995 Edition)
snippet.description:
JumpStart Preschool Full Playthrough (Classic 1995 Edition)

JumpStart Preschool is a game released by Knowledge Adventure in 1995. It would later be replaced by JumpStart Preschool (1999).

In the game, the player accompanies four animal children to preschool. The player can engage in many activities around the school.
